files.preview:
Announcing EDHREC and Card Kingdom Partnership

Urborg, Dominaria - May 5th, 2017 - EDHREC has partnered with Card Kingdom, an online card vendor, to improve pricing data and make it easier to purchase cards from edhrec.com.

Recently, you may have noticed that the prices at the bottom left of cards on edhrec.com changed to hyperlinks where before they didn't. When you click on these links now, they take you directly to their respective page on cardkingdom.com, making it easier to purchase cards you find on edhrec.com. Also, we get the prices displayed on the cards directly from Card Kingdom.
